{"tid":2178234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最後倒數 請大家幫幫陣地社工","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T09:24:12.000Z","uid":178387,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"99387c8a132631d89965c2cda458615462cb7655","tid":2178234,"uid":178387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:02:02.000Z","msg":"得返最後3日，但眾籌仲差幾十萬，如果各位能力所及，希望可以幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/battlefieldswfunding01/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fbattlefieldswfunding01%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=eb92f107\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/battlefieldswfunding01/</a><br />\n<br />\n陣地社工於過去一年多在抗爭現場進行人道支援工作，就是努力「守護生命」和「捍衛保安」。<br />\n<br />\n可是，我們5位社總陣地社工和1位社工復興運動社工，於過去一年基於認為生命比執法更重要，在抗爭現場捍衛國防和守護生命，因此受到不同程度的打壓和身體傷害。被判阻差辦公罪成而正進行上訴，社工陳虹秀Jackie被控暴動，社工許麗明Ming被控襲警警，社工鍵被捆綁警察以警棍撲頭，社工何詩敏和劉彥德被票控&ldquo;限聚&rdquo;令」。我們決定除了繼續在抗爭現場進行人道支援工作外，亦會透過法庭判決取回公道，轉換社工於街頭守護公義的必要性和需要性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o1VBF_1TGco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo1VBF_1TGco&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyC%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=31619579\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o1VBF_1TGco</a>"},{"pid":"c79ee5f5b29b7a20889a85bdff99fd91eb705a39","tid":2178234,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:05:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a10f374e299bcc78535dd5b15a6b62e56ffa6ad1","tid":2178234,"uid":102255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9eb3c8c541921f0cdf9791c8767cf28747fc8da","tid":2178234,"uid":93717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41dfb5d6cebe63ede8fd9960799f9aa86b279bff","tid":2178234,"uid":178387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T13:40:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e174fb2503c69f08f91da73eb2b9cc13799ffed","tid":2178234